<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-particles3d-particleshape3d.xml">ParticleShape3D</db:link> element supports shapes like <db:code>Cube</db:code>, <db:code>Sphere</db:code> and <db:code>Cylinder</db:code> for particles needs. For example, emitter can use <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-particles3d-particleemitter3d.xml#shape-prop">shape</db:link> property to emit particles from the shape area.</db:para>
<db:para>Shapes don't have position, scale or rotation. Instead, they use parent node for these properties.</db:para>
</db:section>
